---
title: Sri Lankan-Spiced Chicken & Fries with Pear Salad & Garlic Aioli
description: Tonight, we're taking omega-3 rich chicken to the next level with our Sri Lankan-inspired seasoning. Add oven-baked fries and garlic aioli for a touch of creaminess, and you have a nutritionally balanced meal that's simply delicious!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
